      "source": "# Train the XGBoost model\r\nfrom xgboost import XGBRegressor\r\n\r\nmodel = XGBRegressor(\r\n    n_estimators=100,\r\n    max_depth=6,\r\n    learning_rate=0.1,\r\n    random_state=42\r\n)\r\n\r\nmodel.fit(X_train, y_train)",
      "execution_count": 0,
